asset.author: Victorinox AG
asset.hookText: You will be right at the front in every situation with the SwissChamp. The top model among the "Officer's Knives" combines 33 high quality tools with an award-winning design. It is made of 67 individual parts and requires an astonishing 450 steps of fabrication in Ibach/Switzerland.
